extendedInfo.description: You've spent the last week or two talking to someone you've met on an online dating site and you've finally made plans to meet. Next thing you know, some lame excuse comes up preventing them from meeting you, or worse yet, you don't hear from them at all. Or maybe they do show up and look nothing like their pictures. The possibilities are endless.Let this app save yourself or someone else endless amounts of time, keystrokes and disappointment.  This is the Angie's List of online dating!Features:- Search for member reviews across all major online dating sites- Add reviews of members- Get alerted when someone else adds a review for a particular memberwww.lotsoffakes.comOnline Dating Profile Reviews
